Frank Wiziarde https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Wiziarde 0 Frank Oliver Wiziarde (died 1987) was an American actor and television personality who was known primarily for his performances as Whizzo the Clown in the Kansas - Missouri area from the 1950s through the 1980s.
